Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.56,0:02:38.83,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H42&}你总是找着悲伤借口
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.83,0:02:42.23,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&H42&}扮演着女主角 让我憎恨
